      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, boil a kettle</p><p>Peel and roughly chop your<strong> red onion[s]</strong></p><p>Deseed your<strong> pepper[s]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>(scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and roughly chop</p><p>Chop your <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into bite-sized pieces</p>",
