    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve your <strong>tomato</strong> <strong>paste</strong>, <strong>red wine paste</strong> and <strong>chicken</strong> <strong>stock</strong> <strong>mix</strong> in 250ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[325ml]</span> [450ml]</span> <strong>boiled</strong> <strong>water </strong>– this is your <strong>red wine stock</strong></p>",
