    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken has browned, remove it<strong> </strong>from the dish and add the <strong>chopped onion</strong>, <strong>pepper </strong>and <strong>potatoes </strong>with the <strong>remaining dried thyme</strong>, <strong>dried oregano</strong>, <strong>roasted garlic paste </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
